{"tid":2094063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：法庭批司法覆核許可禁止令　阻警搜查李柱銘、黎智英等被告電話","createTime":"2020-07-04T09:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T10:57:21.000Z","uid":22556,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"80450d7dfca35892f5f0fecab68425673041adfc","tid":2094063,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"李柱銘、何俊仁、區諾軒等民主派人士，早前被控 8.18、10.1 和 10.20，參與組織及煽動未經批准集結，警方向各被告發出搜查令，預告會在 7 月 3 日起解鎖他們的電話並搜查；李柱銘、何俊仁、區諾軒、單仲偕及楊森五名被告，今日緊急向等法院申請司法覆核，挑戰警方的搜查令，獲法官批出司法覆核許可，法庭並批出禁止令，禁止警方搜查涉案電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E6%9F%B1%E9%8A%98-%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E7%AD%89%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E6%A1%88-%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%89%B9%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E8%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%BB%A4-%E9%98%BB%E8%AD%A6%E6%90%9C%E6%9F%A5%E5%90%84%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%259F%25B1%25E9%258A%2598-%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E9%2598%25BB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2590%2584%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=9ea37518\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%259F%25B1%25E9%258A%2598-%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%25AD%2589%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8